title: BONUS: Jessie Reyez Opens Up & Gets VERY Honest On Relationships, Family, + Career
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Artist Jessie Reyez came to hang out with Rosenberg and Laura Stylez for an honest conversation about dealing with success, dating, finding inspiration inside her music, self love, acting, helping her family, and more! 

Her latest project 'Yessie' is available now!
